    "created_at": "2014-11-07T00:04:46Z",
    "updated_at": "2014-11-07T00:04:46Z",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "One thing we don't support, that we might consider eventually, is resetting the kernel connection from the beginning (getting a new session, etc.). This is required to reconnect to a server that has restarted. Currently the only way to do this is to refresh the page, but clearing and recreating the Session ought to be sufficient.\n"
